          "><div class="bg-fill-weak space-y-4 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="group border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all text-text-brand bg-fill-brand-weak border-transparent hover:bg-fill-brand-weak active:bg-fill-brand-weak focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:text-text-brand-weak size-12 [&amp;&gt;.state]:size-12 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center disableLinkHover" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#Server"></use></svg></span></div><div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="text-body-large text-text-strong font-bold">All your PDF tools in one place</h3><p class="text-body-default text-text-weak">With PDF Help, there’s no need to switch between apps. Convert, edit, sign, split, and protect your PDF files – all in one simple browser-based platform.</p></div></div><div class="bg-fill-weak space-y-4 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="group border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all text-text-brand bg-fill-brand-weak border-transparent hover:bg-fill-brand-weak active:bg-fill-brand-weak focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:text-text-brand-weak size-12 [&amp;&gt;.state]:size-12 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center disableLinkHover" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#ShieldCheck"></use></svg></span></div><div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="text-body-large text-text-strong font-bold">Privacy you can trust</h3><p class="text-body-default text-text-weak">Your documents stay safe with us. We use secure connections and encryption to protect your data every step of the way. Your privacy is always a priority.</p></div></div><div class="bg-fill-weak space-y-4 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="group border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all text-text-brand bg-fill-brand-weak border-transparent hover:bg-fill-brand-weak active:bg-fill-brand-weak focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:text-text-brand-weak size-12 [&amp;&gt;.state]:size-12 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center disableLinkHover" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#Devices"></use></svg></span></div><div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="text-body-large text-text-strong font-bold">No downloads, no hassle</h3><p class="text-body-default text-text-weak">PDF Help works online on any device – desktop, laptop, tablet, or phone. Whether you&#x27;re using Windows, macOS, iOS, or Android, you can access our tools instantly, anytime, anywhere.</p></div></div><div class="bg-fill-weak space-y-4 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="group border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all text-text-brand bg-fill-brand-weak border-transparent hover:bg-fill-brand-weak active:bg-fill-brand-weak focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:text-text-brand-weak size-12 [&amp;&gt;.state]:size-12 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center disableLinkHover" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#FileUpload"></use></svg></span></div><div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="text-body-large text-text-strong font-bold">Easy to use, no tech skills required</h3><p class="text-body-default text-text-weak">Just upload your file, choose what you want to do, and let PDF Help handle the rest. Our intuitive interface is designed to save you time and make document work effortless.</p></div></div><div class="bg-fill-weak space-y-4 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="group border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all text-text-brand bg-fill-brand-weak border-transparent hover:bg-fill-brand-weak active:bg-fill-brand-weak focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:text-text-brand-weak size-12 [&amp;&gt;.state]:size-12 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center disableLinkHover" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#FaceSmile"></use></svg></span></div><div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="text-body-large text-text-strong font-bold">Fast and reliable results</h3><p class="text-body-default text-text-weak">Need it done quickly? Most tasks take just a few seconds – with high-quality results you can count on. Get your PDFs ready in moments, not minutes.</p></div></div><div class="bg-fill-weak space-y-4 rounded-2xl p-8"><div class="group border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all text-text-brand bg-fill-brand-weak border-transparent hover:bg-fill-brand-weak active:bg-fill-brand-weak focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:text-text-brand-weak size-12 [&amp;&gt;.state]:size-12 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center disableLinkHover" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#Support"></use></svg></span></div><div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="text-body-large text-text-strong font-bold">Real help, when you need it</h3><p class="text-body-default text-text-weak">Got a question or hit a snag? Our support team is here to assist. Friendly, fast, and always ready to help you get back on track.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="bg-fill-brand-weak rounded-2xl p-4 lg:p-12 mt-16 lg:mt-12"><div class="
          flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4
          lg:flex-row lg:justify-between lg:space-y-0
        "><div class="
            space-y-3 text-center
            lg:space-y-2 lg:text-left
          "><h2 class="text-heading3 text-text-strong font-bold">Edit your PDF Now</h2><p class="lg:max-w-[687px]">Our engine makes quick work of file editing for PDFs. Just upload a PDF or other document to get started!</p></div><div role="presentation" tabindex="0"><input accept="application/pdf,.pdf" multiple="" type="file" style="border:0;clip:rect(0, 0, 0, 0);clip-path:inset(50%);height:1px;margin:0 -1px -1px 0;overflow:hidden;padding:0;position:absolute;width:1px;white-space:nowrap" tabindex="-1"/><button class="group rounded-lg border font-semibold transition-colors disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-default [&amp;&gt;.state]:inline-flex [&amp;&gt;.state]:w-full [&amp;&gt;.state]:items-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:justify-center [&amp;&gt;.state]:transition-all border-fill-brand-strong bg-fill-brand-strong text-text-inverse-strong hover:shadow-raised hover:[&amp;&gt;.state]:bg-fill-hover active:[&amp;&gt;.state]:bg-fill-press focus:shadow-raised focus:outline-stroke-focus focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 disabled:bg-fill-disabled disabled:border-transparent text-body-large h-14 [&amp;&gt;.state]:h-14 [&amp;&gt;.state]:px-7 inline-flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer disableLinkHover animate-pulse-shadow w-full max-w-[310px]" data-loading="false"><span class="state relative block"><span class="relative flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="inline self-center size-6"><use href="#Upload"></use></svg>Upload to edit</span></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--$?--><template id="B:1"></template><!--/$--><footer id="footer"><div class="dark"><div class="bg-background-alternate text-text-weak min-h-[var(--footer-height) border-stroke-weak border-t px-6 py-4 max-sm:px-4 md:py-6"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1152px] px-0 lg:px-4"><div class="
