\"title\":\"Join us\"},\"mission\":{\"paragraph1\":\"Vision: Simplifying document management for everyone.\\n Mission: To provide an intuitive and affordable PDF editor that enhances productivity and security for all users, without a learning curve.\",\"paragraph2\":\"We believe that document management should be simple and accessible. That’s why we’ve developed a tool that puts the power of PDF editing directly in your hands - whether you’re annotating, converting, or making text adjustments, PDF Help makes it straightforward and efficient. Our commitment is to create a tool that helps users focus on what truly matters: their work.\",\"title\":\"Our vision \u0026 mission\"},\"title\":\"About Us\"},\"CancelSubscription\":{\"action\":\"Cancel Subscription\",\"confirmation\":{\"cancel\":\"Close\",\"confirm\":\"Cancel Subscription\",\"title\":\"Are you sure you want to cancel?\"},\"description\":\"Easily cancel your subscription by entering the email used to create your account.\",\"email\":{\"label\":\"Your email address\"},\"errors\":{\"noUserFound\":\"No user with an active subscription matches this email\"},\"hint1\":\"If you don't remember which email you used to register, check your inbox for emails from PDF Help. \\nOtherwise, contact our friendly customer support at \u003cemail\u003ehere\u003c/email\u003e.\",\"hint2\":\"You can also cancel your subscription by logging into your account, going to the “Membership” tab and clicking \\\"Cancel Subscription\\\".\",\"noActiveSubscriptionUser\":\"No user with an active subscription matches this email\",\"title\":\"Cancel Subscription\",\"toasts\":{\"error\":{\"description\":\"If this is a mistake, contact our support team\",\"title\":\"No active subscription\"},\"success\":{\"description\":\"You shall not be charged from now on.\",\"title\":\"You are unsubscribed!\"}}},\"components\":{\"backButton\":{\"actionLabel\":\"Leave\",\"cancelLabel\":\"Cancel\",\"description\":\"You will lose all unsaved changes.\",\"title\":\"Are you sure you want to leave this page?\"},\"compressPdfModal\":{\"cta\":\"Compress\",\"level\":{\"balanced\":{\"description\":\"Medium file - good quality\",\"name\":\"Balanced\"},\"finalSize\":\"Final size\",\"low\":{\"description\":\"Largest file - best quality\",\"name\":\"Low\"},\"max\":{\"description\":\"Smallest file - standard quality\",\"name\":\"Maximum\"},\"title\":\"Choose compression level\"},\"loading\":\"Compression in progress\",\"recommended\":\"Recommended\",\"title\":\"Compress PDF\"},\"confirmModal\":{\"destructive\":{\"cancel\":\"Cancel\",\"confirm\":\"Delete\"},\"warning\":{\"cancel\":\"Cancel\",\"confirm\":\"Yes\"}},\"contactUsForm\":{\"email\":{\"label\":\"Email*\"},\"message\":{\"label\":\"Message*\"},\"name\":{\"label\":\"Name*\"},\"send\":\"Send message\",\"subject\":{\"label\":\"Subject*\",\"options\":{\"billing\":\"Billing question\",\"other\":\"Other\",\"suggestion\":\"Suggested improvement\",\"technical\":\"Technical issue\"}},\"successToast\":{\"description\":\"Your message has been sent successfully! Our team will get back to you within the next 2 hours.\",\"title\":\"Message sent\"},\"surname\":{\"label\":\"Surname*\"}},\"date\":{\"today\":\"Today\",\"yesterday\":\"Yesterday\"},\"DocumentsList\":{\"actions\":{\"delete\":{\"confirmation\":{\"cancel\":\"Cancel\",\"confirm\":\"Delete\",\"title\":\"Are you sure you want to delete \u003cdocumentTitle\u003e\u003c/documentTitle\u003e?\"},\"label\":\"Delete\"},\"download\":\"Download\",\"open\":\"Open\"},\"labels\":{\"actions\":\"Actions\",\"date\":\"Date\",\"name\":\"Name\",\"size\":\"Size\"}},\"downloadModal\":{\"cancel\":\"Cancel\",\"description\":\"Select a format to download your document\",\"download\":\"Download\",\"fileName\":{\"label\":\"File name\",\"placeholder\":\"Enter file name\"},\"formats\":{\"doc\":\"DOC\",\"docx\":\"WORD\",\"jpg\":\"JPG\",\"pdf\":\"PDF\",\"png\":\"PNG\",\"ppt\":\"PPT\",\"pptx\":\"PPTX\",\"txt\":\"TXT\",\"xls\":\"XLS\",\"xlsx\":\"EXCEL\"},\"title\":\"All set!\"},\"forgotPassword\":{\"actionLabel\":\"Send password\",\"cancelLabel\":\"Cancel\",\"description\":\"Enter your email and we’ll send your password.\",\"sent\":{\"actionLabel\":\"Done\",\"description\":\"We have sent your password to \u003cemail\u003eEMAIL\u003c/email\u003e.\\nPlease check your email to login.\",\"title\":\"Password sent\"},\"title\":\"Forgot your password?\",\"trigger\":\"Forgot your password?\"},\"GetFormNow\":{\"actionLabel\":\"Get {type} Form\",\"title\":\"Fill {type} in less than 5 minutes\"},\"loader\":{\"convert\":{\"loading\":\"Conversion in progress...\",\"one\":\"Scanning for viruses\",\"three\":\"Getting your file ready\",\"two\":\"Converting your document\"},\"loading\":\"Loading...\",\"split\":{\"loading\":\"Splitting your file...\",\"one\":\"Uploading file\",\"three\":\"Preparing download\",\"two\":\"Splitting pages\"}},\"nutrient\":{\"editor\":{\"redo\":\"Redo\",\"undo\":\"Undo\"}},\"offer\":{\"conversion\":{\"description\":\"Easily convert PDFs to various formats and vice versa, making your documents versatile and accessible.\",\"title\":\"Seamless\\n Conversion\"},\"editing\":{\"description\":\"Edit your PDFs with just a few clicks, without the hassle of complex tools.\",\"title\":\"Effortless\\n Editing\"},\"productivity\":{\"description\":\"Save time with an intuitive interface that minimizes the learning curve while maximizing output.\",\"title\":\"Enhanced\\n Productivity\"},\"results\":{\"description\":\"Create polished and professional-looking documents without requiring advanced skills.\",\"title\":\"Professional\\n Results\"},\"title\":\"What We Offer\"},\"printAndDownload\":{\"download\":\"Download\",\"print\":\"Print\"},\"quickLinks\":{\"edit\":{\"compress\":\"Compress PDF\",\"convert\":\"Convert PDF\",\"delete\":\"Delete pages\",\"edit\":\"Edit PDF\",\"merge\":\"Merge PDF\",\"rotate\":\"Rotate PDF\",\"sign\":\"Sign PDF\",\"split\":\"Split PDF\",\"title\":\"Edit PDF\"},\"forms\":{\"cms1500\":\"CMS-1500\",\"ds11\":\"D