":\"Convert PDF to PowerPoint\",\"pdfToWord\":\"Convert PDF to Word\",\"pngToPdf\":\"Convert PNG to PDF\",\"pptxToPdf\":\"Convert PowerPoint to PDF\",\"rotatePdf\":\"Rotate PDF\",\"signPdf\":\"Sign PDF\",\"splitPdf\":\"Split PDF\",\"wordToPdf\":\"Convert Word to PDF\"}},\"wordToPdf\":{\"featureSteps\":{\"1\":\"Upload your Word file to the upload area.\",\"2\":\"Let PDF Help process and convert it into a PDF.\",\"3\":\"Once finished, download your converted file to your device.\",\"title\":\"Convert Word to PDF in just 3 simple steps\"},\"hero\":{\"bullets\":{\"1\":\"Edit text quickly\",\"2\":\"Keep the same look and layout\",\"3\":\"Add an electronic signature\"},\"mobileDescription\":\"Turn your Word file into PDF format easily\",\"subtitle\":\"Turn your Word file into PDF format easily\",\"title\":\"Convert Word to PDF in seconds\",\"upload\":{\"text\":\"Drop your file here\",\"uploadButtonText\":\"Upload to convert\"}},\"upload\":{\"cta\":\"Upload to convert\",\"description\":\"Start by uploading your document to our online PDF converter.\",\"title\":\"Convert Word to PDF\"}}},\"metadata\":{\"about-us\":{\"description\":\"PDF Help was created to make working with PDFs simple, fast, and free for everyone. Learn more about our mission, values, and the team behind your favorite online PDF tools\",\"ogDescription\":\"At PDF Help, we believe everyone deserves powerful, easy-to-use PDF tools without the hassle. Discover who we are, why we built PDF Help, and what drives us to keep improving.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Get to Know PDF Help - Our Story \u0026 Mission\",\"title\":\"Who We Are \u0026 Why We Built PDF Help | About Us\"},\"cancel-subscription\":{\"description\":\"Need to cancel your PDF Help subscription? We're here to make it easy. Follow simple steps to manage or end your current plan—no hassle, no hidden steps.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Looking to cancel your PDF Help plan? Manage your subscription in just a few clicks. We value your time and make the process clear, quick, and transparent.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Easily Cancel Your PDF Help Subscription\",\"title\":\"Cancel Your PDF Help Subscription | Manage Your Plan\"},\"cms1500-form\":{\"description\":\"Easily complete the CMS-1500 health insurance claim form online with PDF Help. Edit, review, and download your filled form in a clean, professional PDF format.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to submit a healthcare claim? Use PDF Help to fill out the CMS-1500 form quickly and accurately. Save time and ensure correct formatting with our online editor.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Complete Your CMS-1500 Claim Form Online - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Fill Out CMS-1500 Medical Claim Form Online | PDF Help\"},\"compress-pdf\":{\"description\":\"Compress PDF files online in seconds. Reduce file size without losing quality. Fast, secure, high-quality PDF compression—hassle free\",\"ogDescription\":\"Make your PDF files smaller with fast, secure, and high-quality compression. Upload your document and get an optimized PDF in seconds.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Compress PDF Online – Reduce PDF Size Instantly\",\"title\":\"Compress PDF Online | Reduce PDF File Size Fast\"},\"contact-us\":{\"description\":\"Need help or have feedback? Reach out to the PDF Help team—we're ready to answer your questions and support you with anything related to our online PDF tools.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Have questions, feedback, or need assistance? Contact PDF Help and our team will get back to you promptly. We're here to help you get the most out of your PDF experience.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Get in Touch with the PDF Help Team\",\"title\":\"Contact PDF Help | We're Here to Assist You\"},\"default\":{\"description\":\"Edit, merge, compress, and convert PDF files instantly with PDF Help. 100% free, secure, and easy to use—right in your browser. No sign-up needed.\",\"ogDescription\":\"PDF Help makes working with PDFs effortless. Edit text, add images, compress files, and convert PDFs to Word, Excel, or JPG—free and secure, no downloads required.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Edit and Convert PDFs Online - Free with PDF Help!\",\"title\":\"Online PDF Editor \u0026 Converter - Fast \u0026 Free | PDF Help\"},\"delete-page\":{\"description\":\"Remove unwanted pages from your PDF in just a few clicks with PDF Help. Upload your file, select the pages to delete, and download the updated document—secure and easy to use.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to remove pages from a PDF? PDF Help makes it simple. Delete one or multiple pages instantly and get a clean, updated file—no sign-up or software required.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Easily Delete PDF Pages with PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Delete Pages from PDF Online | Simple \u0026 Fast | PDF Help\"},\"ds11-form\":{\"description\":\"Complete the U.S. Passport Application Form DS-11 online with PDF Help. Fill in the form, save your work, and download a ready-to-print PDF—fast, easy, and accurate.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to apply for a U.S. passport? Use PDF Help to fill out the DS-11 form online. Edit securely in your browser and download a clean, printable PDF with all your details.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Fill and Download DS-11 Passport Form - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Fill Out DS-11 Passport Application Form Online | PDF Help\"},\"ds82-form\":{\"description\":\"Renew your U.S. passport with the DS-82 form using PDF Help. Fill it out online, review for accuracy, and download a ready-to-print PDF—quick, secure, and convenient.\",\"ogDescription\":\"PDF Help makes passport renewal easy. Fill out the DS-82 form online, ensure all info is correct, and download your completed document—ready for submission.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Complete Your DS-82 Passport Renewal Form - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Fill Out DS-82 Passport Renewal Form Online | PDF Help\"},\"edit-pdf\":{\"description\":\"Easily edit PDF documents with PDF Help. Add or remove text, insert images, highlight content, and make other changes directly in your browser—no software needed.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to change something in a PDF? PDF Help lets you edit text, images, and layout quickly and securely. All your edits stay in place—just upload, edit, and download.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Edit PDFs Instantly and Easily Online - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Edit PDF Files Online | Add Text, Images \u0026 More | PDF Help\"},\"excel-to-pdf\":{\"description\":\"Convert your Excel spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX) to PDF with PDF Help. Maintain table structure, formatting, and data accuracy—quick, secure, and easy to use.\",\"ogDescription\":\"PDF Help converts Excel files to high-quality PDFs while preserving formulas, charts, and layout. Perfect for reports, invoices, and presentations—no software needed.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Turn Excel Sheets into PDFs Effortlessly - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Convert Excel to PDF Online | Preserve Layout \u0026 Tables | PDF Help\"},\"faq\":{\"description\":\"Find quick answers to the most common questions about using PDF Help. Learn how to edit, convert, sign, and manage your PDF files with step-by-step guidance.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Have a question about how PDF Help works? Browse our FAQ section for helpful information on editing, converting, and managing PDFs—all in one place.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Frequently Asked Questions About PDF Help\",\"title\":\"PDF Help FAQ | Get Answers to Common Questions\"},\"forms\":{\"description\":\"Access a library of popular fillable PDF forms including W-9, DS-11, and more. Download, edit, and complete official documents easily with PDF Help—no printing required.\",\"ogDescription\":\"PDF Help offers a collection of essential forms like W-9, tax forms, and business documents. Fill them out online, save your progress, and export as polished PDFs.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Browse and Fill Common PDF Forms Online - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Download Fillable PDF Forms | W-9, Tax \u0026 Legal Docs | PDF Help\"},\"fw9-form\":{\"description\":\"Easily complete and download the official IRS W-9 form with PDF Help. Fill it out online, save your progress, and get a ready-to-submit PDF—no printing or scanning required.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to fill out a W-9? PDF Help lets you complete the IRS W-9 form right in your browser. Edit, sign, and export a clean, professional PDF in minutes.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Edit and Download Your W-9 Form Online - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Fill Out W-9 Form Online | Editable \u0026 Printable PDF | PDF Help\"},\"home\":{\"description\":\"Edit, merge, compress, and convert PDF files instantly with PDF Help. 100% free, secure, and easy to use—right in your browser. No sign-up needed.\",\"ogDescription\":\"PDF Help makes working with PDFs effortless. Edit text, add images, compress files, and convert PDFs to Word, Excel, or JPG—free and secure, no downloads required.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Edit and Convert PDFs Online - Free with PDF Help!\",\"title\":\"Online PDF Editor \u0026 Converter - Fast \u0026 Free | PDF Help\"},\"i864-form\":{\"description\":\"Fill out USCIS Form I-864 easily with PDF Help. Edit the Affidavit of Support online, review for accuracy, and download a ready-to-submit PDF—secure and efficient.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to sponsor an immigrant? PDF Help helps you complete Form I-864 online. Enter your details, review, and download the official USCIS form as a clean, printable PDF.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Fill Out Form I-864 Affidavit of Support - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Complete Form I-864 Affidavit of Support Online | PDF Help\"},\"i9-form\":{\"description\":\"Easily complete the USCIS Form I-9 for employment verification with PDF Help. Fill, review, and download your form as a professional, ready-to-submit PDF—no printing needed.\",\"ogDescription\":\"Need to verify employment eligibility? Use PDF Help to fill out the I-9 form securely online. Complete Section 1, prepare for Section 2, and export a polished PDF in minutes.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Edit and Download Form I-9 Online - PDF Help\",\"title\":\"Fill Out I-9 Employment Eligibility Form Online | PDF Help\"},\"image-to-pdf\":{\"description\":\"Convert images to PDF instantly with PDFHelp. Upload